welcome to our Repository !! 

We are brainstormers a group of young and motivated students who came together to create a cross-platform application consisting of a web, desktop and mobile 
project.

About our project: 

Web-application : 
-----------------------------------------TECHNOLOGIES-----------------------------------------
- using the symfony 4.4 framework as it's most stable and has all our required bundles.
- creating multiple apis and securing them with the jwt login api with a short life-span token.
- using MySQL as our database.
- using the integrated templates in symfony as our front-office 
